         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[August 1857] ¶ Dear friend,  ¶  ¶ I am sending you Barbados cotton, ¶  a few seeds, and ordinary Gossypium arboreum in larger quantity. I hope you are quite well with your dear family. — Excuse my ha...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">57.08.00</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Friedrich Krichauff</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Private hands.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">[August 1857]<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition</seg> — M was made Director of the Melbourne Botanic Gardens on 13 August 1857, a fact which he mentions in the text of this letter as having recently taken place.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Lieber Freund. </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich sende Dir Barbados Baumwolle ein paar Samen u gewöhnl Gossyp arboreum in grösserer Menge. Ich hoffe Du bist ganz Wohl mit Deiner lieben Familie. — Entschuldige meine Eile. — Ich bin jetzt formell installirt als <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Director</hi>
               </seg> des bot Gartens; u will alles mögliche thun, den Garten in die Höhe zu bringen u die jetzt existirenden 1500 Pfl. in 2 Jahren zu 5000 zu vermehren Bitte sende mir doch eine gute Sammlung euerer Scrub Samen Die jungen Herren Fischer können vielleicht auch ein wenig dazu beitragen. Es wird in meiner Macht liegen, eine grosse Gegengabe zu machen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit treuer Freundschaft</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">[August 1857]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear friend, </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am sending you Barbados cotton,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to D. Moore, 27 July 1857.</p>
               </note> a few seeds, and ordinary <name key="Gossypium%20arboreum">Gossypium arboreum</name> in larger quantity. I hope you are quite well with your dear family. — Excuse my haste.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am now formally installed as <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Director</hi>
               </seg> of the Botanic Garden, and want to do all kinds of things to upgrade the Garden, and increase the current number of 1500 plants to 5000 in the next 2 years.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Please, do send me a good collection of your scrub seeds. The young Mr Fischers<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Sons of Ludwig Fischer.</p>
               </note> can perhaps contribute a little to that as well. It will be in my power to make a large return gift.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">In true friendship</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Gossypium%20arboreum">Gossypium arboreum</name>
            </p>
         </div>
